data.fullContent: The process in all only takes 30 seconds to a minute and is just a swirl around your mouth before brushing your teeth. Do this once every other day, and you should see results within a couple weeks. Take precaution when using Hydrogen Peroxide and be sure not to swallow large doses as this is a chemical and could cause vomiting. It should also be noted that over usage of Hydrogen Peroxide on the teeth can peel away enamel resulting in cavities, so it is important to stick to every other day rather than daily.
data.answer: 这个过程总共只需要30秒到1分钟，而且只是在刷牙前在你的嘴里打转而已。每隔一天这样做一次，几周内你就会看到效果。使用双氧水时要注意，一定不要吞下大剂量的双氧水，因为这是一种化学物质，可能导致呕吐。还需要注意的是，过度使用双氧水会剥落牙齿珐琅质，导致蛀牙，所以每隔一天使用双氧水比每天使用更重要。
